# Types of Packages

Checking your code (linter, git-merge-check)

Modifying your code (prettyfy)

Context menus (color-picker, bezier-curve-editor, snippets, autocomplete-plus)

Decorations
  - git-diff (gutter)
  - bookmarks (for gutter book mark indicators)
  - find-and-replace (for boxes around found search terms)
  - decoration-example
  - file-icons, file-type-color

UI changes
  - mini-map
  - treeview
  - resize-panes
  - git-blame

Input helpers (block-travel, vim-mode)
  - jumpy, easy motion

Viewers (asciidoc-preview, mdpreview, atom-runner)
  - regex-railroad-diagram
  - https://atom.io/packages/stacktrace
  - ask stack overflow
  - git log
  - hex view
  - todo show

Integrations
  - gist-it
  - rdio

Themes
  - https://atom.io/themes/pen-paper-coffee-syntax
